'''Bonemer''' was a synthetic substance used to repair, replace, or supplement [[Bone/Legends|bone]]. [[Ottdefa/Legends|Ottdefa]] [[Osuno Whett/Legends|Osuno Whett]] extended his [[Limb/Legends|limbs]] with bonemer as part of an attempt to change his appearance to avoid the wrath of the [[Renatasian]]s. Bonemer was about the same weight as regular bones, but nearly five times harder.

